data.description: Discover the epitome of comfort and style in this meticulously maintained 5-bed, 3-bath ranch-style home with a basement in the Amberton community, nestled in the city of Powder Springs. Upon entering, bask in the warmth of natural light that fills the home, creating an inviting atmosphere. The formal dining room offers versatility for your lifestyle needs. The open kitchen seamlessly flows into the family room, providing the perfect setting for entertaining or family gatherings. The owner's suite on the main floor level offers a sitting area, two closets for your wardrobe needs, double vanities, and a recently updated shower. Pamper yourself with the convenience of two closets for all your wardrobe needs. Two additional bedrooms on the main floor, accompanied by a convenient laundry room, add to the home's practical layout. The basement is a hidden treasure, offering ample storage, second kitchen, two additional bedrooms, a bathroom, a media area for endless entertainment possibilities, second laundry room, and an inviting outside patio area. The backyard is your oasis, ready for delightful spring and summer nights. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or simply unwinding under the stars, this open space is the perfect canvas for creating lasting memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a viewing today and discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality in this Amberton beauty.
